    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115">Adelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #childOf" ref="#people/3470">Maionis</persName>
                        filii <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115">nostri</persName>, in
                            <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> omnes
                        illas <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Public_exactions #Census #Datium #Exemption"
                            >dationes vel pensiones</rs> quascumque <rs key="#Slave">servis</rs>
                        predicti monasterii ex <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Fiscal_property #Privileges #Exemption" ref="#places/3462"
                            >finibus Campu Bassi</placeName> et ex <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Gai #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/3418">finibus
                            Bifernense</placeName> ad <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            >gastaldi</rs> vel <rs key="#Judge">iudicibus</rs> ex ipsis <rs
                            key="#Villages/settlements">castellis seu locis</rs> persolvere debunt
                            <rs key="#Bonus/Malus_usus">per mala consuetudo</rs>, ita ut nullum
                        gastaldus vel iudex aliqua <rs key="#Datium">datione</rs> eorum tollant vel
                            <rs key="#Angaria">angaria</rs> faciant facere aut quacumque <rs
                            key="#Servitium">laborationes</rs> utilitate sua faciant aut in hoste
                        pergantur, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum
                        roboreum preceptum omnia que superius leguntur predictum monasterium eiusque
                        rectores habere et possidere valeant, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id
                        est comitibus, gastaldiis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam
                        requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideant. Quod vero preceptum
                        concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            ref="#people/3468" key="#Notary">Erchemfrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/3442">Trebento</placeName> vicesimo quinto anno, mense
                        magio, undecima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
